metadata.creator: E. Nesbit
metadata.description:
Five children discover a Psammead, a wish-granting sand-fairy, when they move to the countryside of Britain.


You can also read a copy of 'Five Children And It' by going to the International Children's Digital Library, a joint project of the Internet Archive and University Of Maryland.
metadata.title: Five Children And It

reviews.reviewbody:
The copy of the book uploaded here is simply not readable.
A decent copy of the book (~600MB) is available at 
generation.feedbooks.com/book/1600.pdf , Though it is at its readability best, it does not have pictures.
As for the story, it is a thriller, no doubt.
